title: Dead Walkers (Aircel)
description:
Some more undead action from Aircel. Written by Christopher Weppler and illustrated by John Grigni. A group of humans battle the leader of the undead, Deathbringer. But high above them in earths orbit an alien makes a startling discovery about the origins of the undead plague.

Due to scenes of gore and violence this comes with an ADULT rating.


Released on http://ComicPirates.info
